"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-gallery-2024-12-15-at-kenyas-maasai-olympics-women-run-to-bridge-the-gender-gap\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"In Pictures  Organisers encourage more women to participate in the annual event traditionally dominated by men.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  A crowd erupts in cheers as a young Maasai woman pelts over the finish line, the latest participant in the \\\"Maasai Olympics\\\", a reimagining of a traditional coming-of-age rite in the rolling Kenyan grasses.\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Saturday, hundreds gathered in the Kimana reserve some 200km (120 miles) from the capital, Nairobi, to watch 160 athletes - including 40 young women - compete in the games.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\", \"score\": 0.9999999999054126, \"rank\": 9.28371548826738e-11, \"text\": \"Nairobi\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The young people were taking part in a reinterpretation of the \\\"Olamayio\\\" rites undertaken by young Maasai men to prove their skills, identify their leaders and attract girlfriends.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 3.2873081669424496e-13, \"text\": \"Maasai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the traditional killing of a lion - and exclusion of girls - have been replaced with sporting prowess and increased visibility for women.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Events like these are enjoyable because the girls will notice their talent,\\\" said Valentine Naisimoi, still panting after competing in the 100-metre race.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Naisimoi explained that many women from her community were expected to fit traditional roles.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are just there to be married.\\\"\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 19-year-old, whose ambition is to be like famed Kenyan athlete Mary Moraa, said the races gave women like her a moment to shine - and hope for more opportunity.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"score\": 0.9057399212170069, \"rank\": 0.09771087541169547, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are going to work hard for it and to help them in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The games saw participants sprint or run over grass for distances ranging from 100 to 5,000 metres.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The competitions are sometimes a twist on local customs: in one, athletes must lob wooden clubs - known as \\\"rungus\\\" and used to ward off hyenas - into a small basket for points.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And while women only compete in the 100 and 1,500 metres, plans are afoot to expand the field, said Maasai coordinator Samuel Kaanki.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 3.2873081669424496e-13, \"text\": \"Maasai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need also girls to participate in this,\\\" he stressed, explaining how the traditional male- focused ceremony had been adapted as the community changed.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I go around to education meetings, many ladies ask me why ladies are not participating in this programme,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event was created in 2012 by community leaders and conservation group Big Life Foundation.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Big Life Foundation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The intention was to help preserve the region's lions, which had plummeted from about 30,000 in the 1970s to just over 2,000.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The events have helped, according to the Big Life Foundation, with more than 250 lions now roaming the Amboseli ecosystem from fewer than 20 in the early 2000s.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2323, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Big Life Foundation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\"}, {\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amboseli_National_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amboseli\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amboseli_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amboseli_National_Park\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Runner Stephen Masindet, 21, said the competition was important because it was changing attitudes.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When they see others running, they want to come to train and become champions.\\\"\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": []}]}"